CHINA; CARTER, JIMMY; REAGAN, RONALD; CHINA -- ARMS SALES -- MIDDLE EAST; HUMAN 
RIGHTS -- CHINA; CAMBODIA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- CHINA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
