64-yard touchdown pass play during Chicago's 20-12 win in their NFC playoff 
game. . . ; Photo, (Southland Edition) . . . And Mckinnon then gives a Bear hug 
to Chicago quarterback Mike Tomczak, who threw the first-quarter pass. United 
