<TEXT>
<P>
Our readers wrote letters throughout 1988 expressing their viewpoints on a 
variety of issues. Here are condensed versions of some of those letters. We 
appreciate their taking the time to share their viewpoints and look forward to 
hearing from you in 1989. 
</P>
<P>
 Let's look at growth in Orange County as if we all had a stake in tomorrow. 
</P>
<P>
One way or another, our children are going to pay for the countless ills 
brought about by unwise development. There's still time, however, to move into 
the next century with style. 
</P>
