HOCKEY CHAMPIONSHIPS; USSR -- ATHLETICS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010190-0053 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 156274 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 1, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
