too. STEVE DYKES / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Celebs and commoners in China 
Club's Monday night crowd share more than usual: casual dress and wanting to 
hear musicians jam for fun. STEVE DYKES / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
