<SUBJECT>
<P>
LUMSDEN, ANTHONY; DANIEL MANN JOHNSON &amp; MENDENHALL; HYPERION SEWAGE 
TREATMENT PLANT; TILLMAN WATER RECLAMATION PLANT; ARCHITECTURE; ARCHITECTS 
</P>
