who likes to march. I really loved to march.' Besides, 'You don't get to see 
the parade, all that happens back there.' JOSE GALVEZ / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Shirley Temple Black giving interviews in Tournament House. ROSEMARY 
KAUL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, As a child film star, Shirley Temple charmed 
millions. United Press International; Photo, "Night of 100 Roses" -- Rose Queen 
Charmaine Shryock dances with Pasadena Mayor Bill Thomson at 100th anniversary 
of Tournament of Roses party Saturday at Pasadena Playhouse. DOUGLAS R. BURROWS 
