<P>
Soap Gets New Intro: "All My Children," ABC's popular daytime drama, will 
celebrate its 20th year on the air by revamping the show's introduction for the 
first time in the soap's history. The "updated" introduction, scheduled to 
debut today, features modern theme music accompanying photos of the core Martin 
family and individual pictures of the cast being entered into a photo album. As 
the final portrait is added, the title "All My Children" floats on screen, and 
