<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski won $80 Monday when his pick in the seventh 
race, Weldnaas, finished first and paid $5.20. Bob wagered $50 to win on 
Weldnaas and his mythical bankroll, which started at $1,000, is now at $1,182. 
</P>
<P>
Monday's Bankroll: $1,102 
</P>
<P>
Monday's Profit: $80 
</P>
<P>
